About BlackCandles
Welcome to BlackCandles, your premier destination for high-quality candles and candle holders. Founded in 2022, we are a passionate team dedicated to bringing warmth, elegance, and tranquility into your space through our carefully curated collection of candles and accessories.

Who We Are
BlackCandles is a brand under Green Park Fudou Dou Trading Co., Ltd., based in Changchun City, Jilin Province, China. Though we are a small team of two, our commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction drives everything we do.

